              <text><emphasis style="italic">Clause 69</emphasis> consequentially amends section 172KB (which requires industry participants to co-operate with Commission investigations). The amendment extends the provision to apply to investigations carried out for the purposes of monitoring or enforcing <emphasis style="italic">new Part 6A</emphasis>.</text>
            </para>
          </clause.desc>
          <clause.desc>
            <para>
              <text><emphasis style="italic">Clause 70</emphasis> consequentially amends section 172O (which relates to the functions of the Commission).</text>
            </para>
