              </amend>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">6</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 21(3) is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">independent</amend.in> in each place where it appears and substituting in each case <amend.in quote="1">international</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
          <subprov skeleton="no">
            <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">7</label>
            <para>
              <text>Section 21(3) is amended by inserting <amend.in quote="1">in relation to Kyoto units</amend.in> after <quote.in quote="1">a transaction</quote.in>.</text>
            </para>
